This study examines the association of dopamine varicosities with post-
synaptic specializations using immuno-electron microscopy and ﬂuor-
escent imaging in striatal slices. It establishes that dopamine varicosities
synapse onto GABA-ergic postsynaptic structures that contain neuroligin
2, and that ELKS2/CAST and neurexin are present in the presynapse.
